          "id": "ee1c63857b3b_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1d70",
          "text": "… Morag and I also shared a little of our own plans for next steps. We both realised that we want to work even harder on making the movement more visible to itself and encourage everyone to amplify each other’s messages and work. We agreed that we need to build an even more diverse movement able to co-create while valuing our diversity as a source of creativity rather than a potential for conflict.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
